      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/images/stories/flexicontent/item_807_field_41/original/jimmymoore-taylorswift-moncton-700x460--1-.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/genid/cc365cd379f14472"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/organizer": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/genid/313e60a9a137ea3c"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/en/tickets-events/jimmy-moore-drag"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Jimmy Moore Drag"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Jimmy Moore Drag"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Relive the Magic of the Eras Tour of Taylor Swift!\r\nCalling all Moncton Swifties!\r\nJimmy Moore Drag is Canada's own Taylor Swift!\r\n3-hour show25 costume changes60,000 audience members\r\nIn June 2023, Quebec’s famed Celebrity Impersonator unveiled his tribute show dedicated to Taylor Swift, and it was an instant hit, selling out immediately.\r\nBut it was in August, at the Montreal Pride Festival, where his recognition soared to new heights. Selling out once again, he solidified his reputation, showing that his portrayal of Taylor Swift – swiftly becoming a living legend – was indeed his magnum opus.\r\nA journalist from the Toronto Sun Times, who witnessed the spectacle, hailed Jimmy as the definitive Canadian Taylor Swift act, exclaiming, “Jimmy Moore is Taylor Swift! His performance quality is unparalleled!” LCN chimed in as well, dubbing him the “Taylor Swift of Quebec.”\r\nIn the show, Jimmy doesn’t stand alone. A skilled ensemble of dancers and a meticulously designed set underscore his performance, collectively lifting the tribute to extraordinary heights.\r\nDrawing inspiration from the Eras Tour of pop’s reigning queen, Jimmy has firmly established himself as the go-to Taylor Swift impersonator.\r\nFor Swifties missing out on the singer’s iconic tour, Jimmy offers the next best thing.\r\nPlatinum VIP&nbsp;Includes M&amp;G + photo backstage before the show + exclusive giftGold VIP Includes an exclusive gift "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Revivez la magie de la tournée Eras de Taylor Swift !\r\nAppel à tous les Swifties de Moncton!\r\nJimmy Moore Drag est la Taylor Swift canadienne!\r\nSpectacle de 3 heures25 changements de costumes60 000 spectateurs\r\nEn juin 2023, le célèbre imitateur québécois a dévoilé son spectacle hommage à Taylor Swift, qui a connu un succès immédiat et s'est vendu en un clin d'œil.\r\nMais c'est en août, lors du Festival de la fierté gaie de Montréal, que sa notoriété a atteint de nouveaux sommets. Une fois de plus à guichets fermés, il a consolidé sa réputation, démontrant que son interprétation de Taylor Swift, en passe de devenir une légende vivante, était bel et bien son chef-d'œuvre.\r\nUn journaliste du Toronto Sun Times, qui a assisté au spectacle, a salué Jimmy comme l’ultime imitateur canadien de Taylor Swift, s'exclamant : «&nbsp;Jimmy Moore est Taylor Swift! La qualité de sa performance est inégalée!&nbsp;» LCN s'est également joint au concert de louanges, le surnommant «&nbsp;La Taylor Swift du Québec&nbsp;».\r\nDans le spectacle, Jimmy n'est pas seul. Une troupe de danseurs talentueux et un décor méticuleusement conçu soulignent sa performance, élevant collectivement l'hommage à des sommets extraordinaires.\r\nS'inspirant de la tournée Eras de la reine incontestée de la pop, Jimmy s'est imposé comme l'imitateur incontournable de Taylor Swift.\r\nPour les Swifties qui ont raté la tournée emblématique de la chanteuse, Jimmy offre la meilleure alternative possible.\r\nPlatinum VIP&nbsp;Inclut M&amp;G + photo backstage avant le spectacle + cadeau exclusifGold VIP inclut un cadeau exclusif "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
