        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "35 ans… Et je cherche encore celebrates the album that, in 1990, introduced Laurence Jalbert to the public and established her voice as one of the most distinctive in Quebec. Driven by songs that have since become emblematic, including Tomber, Rage, Les yeux noirs, À toi, En courant and Au nom de ..."
