    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Damien Robitaille"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Damien Robitaille"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Damien Robitaille lights up the stage with boundless charisma and remarkable versatility, effortlessly jumping between instruments and musical styles. Beloved not only for his magnetic live performances but also for his wildly popular and inventive social media presence, Robitaille has captivated a massive online audience with his humour, creativity, and infectious energy — earning fans far beyond the concert hall.\r\nFrom catchy singalongs to heartfelt ballads, he knows how to draw audiences in, creating a vibrant connection where spontaneity, warmth, and pure joy take centre stage. Both intimate and high-energy, his performances sweep audiences into a whirlwind of rhythm, laughter, and celebration.\r\nWith every song, Damien crafts a festive atmosphere where music and togetherness collide, turning the night into an unforgettable shared experience overflowing with emotion, energy, and feel-good spirit.\r\nPerformance in French. "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Damien Robitaille éblouit son public avec sa polyvalence, jonglant avec virtuosité entre les instruments et les styles musicaux. Des refrains entraînants aux ballades poignantes, il sait comment captiver son auditoire et créer une atmosphère où règnent la complicité et la bonne humeur. Une expérience musicale à la fois intime et énergique.\r\nDamien vous transporte dans un tourbillon de joie et de bonne humeur, créant ainsi une ambiance festive où la musique et la convivialité se mêlent pour créer des instants de pur bonheur. "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ]
  },
