    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Forever Seger"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Forever Seger"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "VaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present:\r\nA TRIBUTE TO THE MUSIC OF BOB SEGER\r\nFOREVER SEGER creates a dynamic journey through the timeless music of Bob Seger and The Silver Bullet Band. With authentic vocals, a 9-piece band and commanding performances, gives that unmistakable Seger sound. FOREVER SEGER’s fast growing reputation as THE Bob Seger tribute experience, has propelled them onto the top-ranking concert stages and festivals across North America.\r\nFrom the opening notes of the timeless classic Turn the Page&nbsp;to Rock and Roll anthems such as Hollywood Nights, Old time Rock and Roll, and Night Moves, it’s clear why Bob Seger fans are calling FOREVER SEGER a true concert experience that invites audiences to dance and sing along once again to the soundtrack of their lives. "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "VaughnCo Entertainment est fier de présenter :\r\nFOREVER SEGER, L’ULTIME HOMMAGE À BOB SEGER ET AU SILVER BULLET BAND.\r\nL’incroyable formation de neuf musiciens de Forever Seger propose un voyage dynamique à travers la musique intemporelle de Bob Seger et du Silver Bullet Band. Grâce à des voix authentiques, des performances captivantes et ce son Seger inimitable, la réputation grandissante de Forever Seger comme expérience hommage à Bob Seger propulse le groupe sur les scènes de concerts et festivals les plus prestigieux d’Amérique du Nord.\r\nDès les premières notes du classique intemporel, Turn the Page jusqu’aux hymnes rock tels que Hollywood Nights , Old Time Rock and Roll et Night Moves, il est clair pourquoi les fans de Bob Seger considèrent Forever Seger comme une véritable expérience de concert qui invite le public à danser et à chanter de nouveau sur la trame sonore de leur vie. "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ]
  },
