        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Maude Landry brings her brilliantly offbeat humour and razor-sharp wit to the stage in a show that is as quirky as it is hilarious. In a world obsessed with fitting in and staying trendy, Maude wonders why she’s never quite belonged to the “cool crowd” — and that’s exactly what makes her so ..."
