      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/sameAs": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/en/tickets-events/patrice-lecuyer"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/location": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/genid/8dd99b1f6916b4e3"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/images/stories/flexicontent/item_978_field_41/original/patrice-lecuyer-intro--1-.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/genid/321a3f789a1bc3cb"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/organizer": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/genid/313e60a9a137ea3c"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://capitol.nb.ca/en/tickets-events/patrice-lecuyer"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Patrice L'Ecuyer"
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Patrice L'Ecuyer"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/inLanguage": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": ""
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "After more than three decades in the spotlight, beloved entertainer Patrice L’Écuyer finally steps onto the stage alone for the very first time with his debut one-man show, Après seulement 32 ans d’absence sur scène.\r\nBest known for his sharp comedic timing and long-running presence in Québec entertainment, from multiple appearances in Bye Bye television productions and iconic hosting roles, to memorable performances in major comedy galas and stage productions, L’Écuyer has spent a career making audiences laugh. Now, he takes on stand-up like never before, fully solo and completely unfiltered.\r\nIn this new show, he opens the door on a life he has long kept private, revisiting unexpected encounters, behind-the-scenes moments, and extraordinary situations involving both loved ones and public figures. With a fast-paced stream of self-deprecating stories and surprising revelations, he transforms his personal history into a comedy experience full of heart and punch.\r\nA former star of the Ligue nationale d’improvisation and one of its most frequently penalized players, L’Écuyer now channels that same fearless energy into a performance where he can finally say everything.\r\nCharismatic, sharp, and delightfully unpredictable, he delivers a show built on storytelling mastery, comic instinct, and the joy of surprising an audience at every turn.\r\nPerformance in French. "
      },
      {
        "@language": "fr",
        "@value": "Patrice L’Ecuyer présente son tout premier one-man-show intitulé Après seulement 32 ans d’absence sur scène. L’humour a toujours occupé une grande place dans sa carrière, que ce soit dans les Bye Bye (comédien dans quatorze éditions!), L’Ecuyer, Prière de ne pas envoyer de fleurs, les galas Juste pour Rire et ComediHa! ou encore le spectacle Merci beaucoup. Mais aujourd’hui, l’animateur chéri depuis trois décennies s’attaque seul à la scène pour la toute première fois!\r\nAu fil de sa carrière, Patrice a toujours été discret sur sa vie, même s’il a vécu des situations hors du commun tant avec ses proches qu’avec de grandes personnalités… mais sur scène, il va tout dévoiler! Flash-back sur sa vie, sa carrière, ses rencontres : à travers un impressionnant flot d’anecdotes remplies d’autodérision, Patrice déploie son immense talent comique. Ancienne star de la LNI (et l’un des joueurs les plus punis!), il a maintenant toute la liberté qu’il faut pour faire rire, surprendre et se mettre à nu sans se sentir coupable. Son talent de conteur, son charisme et ses propos surprenants feront de son spectacle un incontournable de la scène humoristique québécoise. "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ],
