        "@value": "Hailing from Montréal’s South Shore, Roxane Bruneau first captured attention online with her sharp, comedic social media sketches before revealing the full depth of her musical talent to the wider public. Her breakout debut album Dysphorie (2017), certified Platinum, launched a meteoric rise and ..."
